Pealr and Rose Gold Plated Earrings.

Delicate white pearls hang from elegantly curved ear wires, giving these earrings an ultra modern touch. The rose gold plating adds an extra sun-kissed glow to your cheeks. 8mm cultured pearl, rose gold plating, 925 silver base. Approximately 2.1 inches long.
fields.name: Classic Blush Earrings

fields.description:
Mother of Pearl and Rose Gold Plated Ring. 

Who says you need gemstones to dazzle? This breathtaking white mother of pearl shell ring is sure to make your skin glow with its bold oval design and warm rose gold plated band. Mother of pearl, rose gold plating, 925 silver base. Approximately 1.25 inches by .6 inch mother of pearl shell.
fields.name: Classic Blush Oval Ring

fields.description:
Mother of Pearl and Rose Gold Plated Ring.

This is the perfect modern ring for any romantic.  Sweet, feminine, and classy, it showcases a luminous white mother of pearl shell set in a spherical, sun-kissed rose gold plated frame. Mother of pearl, rose gold plating, 925 silver base. Approximately .75 inch mother of pearl shell.
fields.name: Classic Blush Round Ring

fields.description:
Amethyst Gemstones and Gold Plated Earrings.

A stunning intricate gold lace filigree is inset with a flurry of precious purple amethyst gemstones, giving these earrings the perfect amount of sparkle and glam. Add them to your outfit for extra vibrancy and pop. Purple Amethyst Gemstones, Gold-Plated 925 Silver. Approximately 1.25 inches long.
fields.name: Gold Confetti Lace Amethyst Earrings

fields.description:
Amethyst Gemstones and Gold Plated Ring.

Allow your inner goddess to shine through with this exquisite amethyst set ring. The gemstones are elegantly twisted into an sinuous curve for that ultimate sexy statement look. Purple Amethyst Gemstone, Gold-Plated 925 Silver. Ring is approximately .5 inches high.
fields.name: Gold Confetti Twist Amethyst Ring

fields.description: Uniqueness is the perfect code word for this dress. Swiss in origin, this bodice fabric has been embroidered with fuzzy yarn colors to offer a true textured look. The skirt has over 100 strips of bias cut organza with colors matching the bodice. It requires 2 days to sew one dress. Fully Lined.
fields.name: Alexandra Dress

fields.description: This Italian Copper / Nutmeg Organic Jacquard dress is inspired by the classic coat shape. The fabric is finished on both sides, offering us the ability to incorporate the positive – negative richness of the design. Fully Lined.
fields.name: Alexis Dress

fields.description: This Swiss 100% Silk was woven into a floral Jacquard of roses. The richness of the color shading gives it a very true to life feeling. Asymmetric in design, flattering placement of the pleated wrap, this dress is perfect for a cocktail look or evening event. Fully Lined.
fields.name: Angelica Dress

fields.description: This Pewter tulle dress is a true collector’s piece with embroidered yarn in a floral design. Beautiful & intricate yarn was embroidered by hand on both the tulle and the black silk shantung skirt. Satin piping was used to accent the princess seams and neckline. Fully Lined.
fields.name: Applique Dress

fields.description: This Wisteria silk dress is a modern take on a toga. Shaped with princess seams & synched at the waist with a self-belt – it is a truly wearable silhouette. Layers of ruffles at the skirt add a glamorous look for any occasion. Each dress takes a full day to put together. Fully Lined.
fields.name: Athena Dress

fields.description: This is a true collector’s piece. Incorporating Italian Black Shantung with Swiss embroidered organza, we gave the ball gown a new twist. Hand application of cut out circles from the skirt gives a sophisticated and elegant look. A belted waist offers a synched style. Fully Lined.
fields.name: Audrey Dress

fields.description: This Paprika silk georgette classically cut shift dress has been spiced up with strategically placed ruffled strips. This belted style allows for synching of the waist and the ruffles are eye catching and lead to a surprisingly slim look. Fully Lined.
fields.name: Bette Dress

fields.description: Bette Dress
fields.name: Bette Dress

fields.description: Taking Swiss multi dot jacquard, we crafted this fun and spirited dress which has a leather waistband and sweeping flared 4 ply crepe skirt which is longer in the back for a new take on a modern style. We added a layer of organza to the skirt for more drama. Fully Lined.
fields.name: Charlotte Dress

fields.description: Uniqueness is the perfect code word for this dress. Swiss in origin, this bodice fabric has been embroidered with fuzzy yarn colors to offer a true textured look. The skirt has over 100 strips of bias cut organza with colors matching the bodice. It requires 2 days to sew one dress. Fully Lined.
fields.name: Countess Dress

fields.description: This hand-crafted work of art is a true collector’s piece. The bodice is constructed of both Shantung and embroidered Jacquard organza. The skirt has over 100 strips strategically placed to give that red carpet look. One dress requires days to put together. Fully Lined.
fields.name: Demi Dress

fields.description: Taking Italian square geometric Jacquard, we gave the volume skirt style a new twist. Feminine short sleeves and a belted waist offer a synched style while elongating the figure. Fully Lined.
fields.name: Duchess Dress

fields.description: Nutmeg Wool from Switzerland is crafted into this ¾ sleeve dress, with pleating and ruffling strategically placed to emphasize an elongated slimming figure. Satin facing offers a glimpse of shine and a classic elegance that is both sophisticated and timeless. Fully Lined.
fields.name: Electra Dress

fields.description: Electra Dress
fields.name: Electra Dress

fields.description: This Italian Jacquard was woven into a geometric collection of squares. The color is a modern blend of Black, Silver and Paprika. Asymmetric in design, flattering placement of the pleated wrap, this dress is perfect for a cocktail look or evening event. Fully Lined.
fields.name: Empress Dress

fields.description: Taking Swiss multi dot jacquard, we crafted this fun and spirited dress which has satin piping at the princess seams. The pleat detail at the skirt offers flair to take this look from the office directly into the evening. We incorporated the same pleat detail in the sleeve. Fully Lined.
fields.name: Galactic Dress

fields.description: This Italian Copper / Nutmeg Organic Jacquard dress is inspired by the classic trench coat. Double breasted with a beautiful collar detail. The sleeves offer 3 tiers of glamour while the inside offers a peak at our craftsmanship. Unlined
fields.name: Meryl Dress

fields.description: This Black & Silver Tweed Dress is a true collector’s piece. A slim shift dress fit ends in an Italian leather flounce. Beautiful and intricate leather ovals and circles were hand cut & embroidered onto the tweed bodice with silver thread matching the tweed. Fully Lined
fields.name: Soho Dress

fields.description: This eye catching Italian Dot Jacquard from Italy is sharply contrasted by Sapphire 4 Ply Crepe, strategically placed at the waist and bordering trim. The dress offers a slenderizing silhouette with elegant lacing detail at the back offering an Elizabethan twist. Fully Lined.
fields.name: Starlight Dress

fields.description: This Swiss 100% Silk was woven into a floral Jacquard of roses. The richness of the color shading gives it a very true to life feeling. Shaped with princess seams and a pleated flair skirt, we added elegant ruffles at the neckline and skirt seam to give a true couture look. Fully Lined.
fields.name: Wisteria Dress

fields.description: Chic, elegant and sophisticated. This dress is well constructed and perfect for any formal occasion.perfect for any formal occasion. perfect for any formal occasion. Made in America.
fields.name: Vera Dress
